                              </div>
                            </div><br>

                            <p>Icons were used are:</p>
                            <img id="test" class="img-responsive" src="img/qtoniq/icon.png" alt=""/><br>

                            <p>All the interactions are captured in the following video:</p><br>
                            <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/231213793" width="640" height="800" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe><br><br>

                            <p>A good logo always transcends the right message about the company and its area of functionality.
                              For this project, I wanted to design a simple logo without any convoluted curves or shadows.
                              I sketched many ideas on the paper and finally decided something which was intuitive and simple. As
                              our focus was on displaying quality quotes, I used the word Q inside the quotation marks with closing
                              quotation mark on the right bottom.</p>
                            <p>It represents <span style="font-size:20px; color:#e8d008">Q</span>uality <span style="font-size:20px; color:#e8d008">Q</span>uotes.</p>
                            <p>The final logo looked like this:</p>
                            <div class="row">
                              <div class="intro col-md-4 col-sm-12  ">
